data.description: Charming starter home in Waite Park neighborhood. This cozy gem offers move-in ready conditions, character, and many updates, all at an affordable price point. Updates include -- refinished wood floors, new windows, AC, washer & dryer. Exterior updates include siding, roof, gutters. Room to add square footage in lower level.  Close to fun -- parks, breweries, distilleries, Mississippi River, eateries all nearby.
